title: Elvis Presley - I Got Lucky
description:
I Got Lucky is a compilation album by Elvis Presley. The album, released in October 1971, is a follow-up to the "C'mon Everybody" album as it features the remaining tracks from the soundtrack EP's (previously unissued on LP) of the same four films from the first compilation plus one non-movie/non-LP track. It was certified Gold on January 6, 2004 and Platinum on September 15, 2011 by the RIAA.[1]
